mmc: sdhci-omap: Add sdhci_omap specific ops for enable_sdio_irq

Add sdhci_omap_enable_sdio_irq to set CTPL and CLKEXTFREE bits in
MMCHS_CON register required to detect asynchronous card interrupt
on DAT[1].

